 <chunk id="ch81" type="p">
  <sentence id="s81">
   <tok>
    <orth>Art</orth>
    <lex disamb="1"><base>Art</base><ctag>ign</ctag></lex>
   </tok>
   <ns/>
   <tok>
    <orth>.</orth>
